  <div class="fs-row equalize">
    <div class="fs-cell fs-lg-3 fs-md-2 fs-sm-3 fs-contained equalize-child">
      <img src="assets/jeni.jpg" class="img-responsive">
    </div>
    <div class="fs-cell fs-lg-9 fs-md-4 fs-sm-3 fs-right fs-contained">
      <div class="page-header-wrapper bg--teal equalize-child">
        <span class="page-header-subtitle bottom">Our student loan expert Jeni Burkhart will answer your most pressing questions about student loan debt and repayment.</span>
        <p class="page-header-desc">
          You and other Tuition.io members can submit questions about student loan debt,
          and our student loan expert will answer 1-2 questions per week. Keep checking back
          here to stay-up-to-date on  tips and tricks for managing your student loan debt.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
